trans-unit.source: Invocation on Dictionary can be simplified
trans-unit.target: Invocation on Dictionary can be simplified
trans-unit.note: An optional longer localizable description of the diagnostic.

trans-unit.source: 'IDictionary<,>' offers a 'ContainsKey' method which should be preferred instead of accessing the 'Keys' property and calling 'Contains' on that
trans-unit.target: 'IDictionary<,>' offers a 'ContainsKey' method which should be preferred instead of accessing the 'Keys' property and calling 'Contains' on that
trans-unit.note: The format-able message the diagnostic displays.

trans-unit.source: 'ContainsKey' does not incur the same overhead as calling the LINQ 'Contains' method on the 'Keys' collection.
trans-unit.target: 'ContainsKey' does not incur the same overhead as calling the LINQ 'Contains' method on the 'Keys' collection.

trans-unit.source: 'ContainsValue' does not incur the same overhead as calling the LINQ 'Contains' method on the 'Values' collection.
